On-Premises Private CloudOn-Premises Private Cloud
Hosted within an organization's own data center.
Provides full control over hardware, security, and compliance.
Suitable for organizations requiring high security and strict regulatory compliance.

Choosing a private cloud deployment strategy depends on security, cost, and scalability needs:

On-Premises Private Cloud:
Full control, high security.

Hosted Private Cloud:
Managed infrastructure, reduced maintenance.

Virtual Private Cloud (VPC):
Secure private network in the public cloud.

Hybrid Private Cloud:
Best of both private and public cloud.
